rows.label: bf05350100_0020
rows.name:
It seems that Senator Roderich entered the Holy See
unofficially last night

rows.label: bf05350100_0040
rows.name:
No...
I haven't been told anything by His Majesty.

rows.label: bf05350100_0050
rows.name:
What business does he have here at this time?
It doesn't seem like just a pilgrimage.

rows.label: bf05350100_0060
rows.name:
Do you think it's something to do with
the excavation? Temperantia?

rows.label: bf05350100_0070
rows.name: Hmm. The issue His Majesty mentioned?

rows.label: bf05350100_0080
rows.name:
If that's the case,
the purpose is to curry favor with the Holy See...
